OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy this
OL,6,Fevening with outbreaks of rain in the
OL,7,Fwest, pushing slowly eastwards
OL,8,Fovernight and reaching most of the
OL,9,Fcountry by dawn. Some snow is also
OL,10,Fpossible over the top of Yr Wyddfa.
OL,11,FTurning breezy along the coasts and
OL,12,Fhills.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FCloudy with rain to start.
OL,15,FRain gradually easing during the
OL,16,Fmorning, and mainly affecting eastern
OL,17,Fparts in the afternoon. Meanwhile,
OL,18,Fsome brighter spells arriving into the
OL,19,Fwest. Feeling cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
