OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FOccasional patchy rain and drizzle in
OL,7,Fplaces, but mostly dry albeit often
OL,8,Fcloudy. Cloud breaking at times to
OL,9,Fgive some sunshine. Temperatures
OL,10,Fcloser to average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
